# E2e tests run in CI, not locally.
#
# The acceptance gate workflow (.github/workflows/acceptance-gate.yml)
# runs full end-to-end tests with real LLM calls against the complete
# system. These are triggered on PR creation and run in GitHub Actions
# where API keys are available via repository secrets.
#
# Local integration tests (test/**/*.integration.test.ts) cover real
# Weaver binary interactions but are a separate tier — they mock other
# dependencies and don't make LLM calls.
